text:
No one should be buying their kids anything like an iPad or iPhone (or whatever Android equivalent). Smart devices are one of the reasons kids are becoming more stupid these days, starting them early in the rubbish the internet provides (aka, ticktock, instagram etc).

I got my first phone when I was a teenager, it was a dumb phone that could call and text. My kids, will get the same. A dumb phone that can call and text.

If they want an expensive device, they can wait till they can work for it and pay for it themselves. My kids will have:

Heavily restricted and monitored internet access,

No instagram
No tick tock
No anti-social media in general until their brains are developed enough where they can make their own rational decisions. Where they won't care if someone says something offensive on the internet to them.
